dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Palo Escrito Peak quadrangle, Monterey County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depths shown by isolines and soundings.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Palo Escrito Peak CA 1956. Photorevised 1984. DMA 1756 IV NW, series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
